This example need Qt version less than the below reported bug in Qt
https://bugreports.qt.io/browse/QTBUG-59001

I tested this on Qt 5.6 and it works fine.

On Qt 5.8 it gives the below error.
=> qt.qpa.cocoa.window: NSView is not QNSView, consider checking for Qt::ForeignWindow

